SMS,Freedom,is,a,bulk,text,messaging,service,that,allows,customers,to,send,numerous,text,SMS,messages,to,groups,at,one,time,Messages,can,be,sent,via,web,interfaces,mobiles,SMTP,and,SMPP,platforms,The,SMS,Freedom,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,and,information,from,SMS,Freedom,Some,example,API,methods,include,sending,messages,receiving,confirmation,of,messages,sent,accessing,delivery,status,and,pushing,messages,out